{
  "_comment": [
    "The single 'dinify-prod' hosting site lives under the 'dinify-dev' Firebase",
    "project. The project name is misleading — it is not limited to development",
    "use. Do NOT rename the project or target without updating the deploy-prod.yml",
    "workflow and coordinating with the team.",
    "",
    "The 'targets' block maps the deploy target name 'dinify-prod' to the Firebase",
    "hosting site 'dinify-prod'. 'dinify-prod' is the live, CI-deployed target: it",
    "is referenced by the deploy-prod.yml GitHub Actions workflow, which deploys on",
    "every merge to main. The legacy 'dinify-dev', 'dinify-stage', and 'dinify-uat'",
    "hosting sites have now been removed from this config; 'dinify-prod' is the sole",
    "hosting target."
  ],
  "projects": {
    "default": "dinify-dev",
    "prod": "dinify-dev"
  },
  "targets": {
    "dinify-dev": {
      "hosting": {
        "dinify-prod": [
          "dinify-prod"
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
